7 Run MiCBuS
The primary call uses an installed MiCBuS package if it is present and exposes a recognizable exported function. If not, the tutorial falls back to the core teaching idea: generate Dirichlet pseudo-bulk mixtures from the incomplete reference and identify genes higher in TCGA bulk tumors than in those mixtures.

common_genes &lt;- Reduce(intersect, list(rownames(bulk_expr), rownames(incomplete_profiles)))
bulk_for_micbus &lt;- bulk_expr[common_genes, , drop = FALSE]
ref_for_micbus &lt;- incomplete_profiles[common_genes, , drop = FALSE]

micbus_res &lt;- run_micbus(
  bulk_expr = bulk_for_micbus,
  incomplete_reference = ref_for_micbus,
  n_reps = n_pseudobulk,
  seed = params$seed
)

